      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though there are minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small surface scratch on the passenger door that are visible upon close inspection. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, showing only light wear on the driver's side seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is solid with a consistent service history, though it will likely need new tires within the next 5,000 miles. It is a reliable, honest car that performs well and is ready for its next owner.",
