      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, preserved in a state that rivals its original showroom debut. This vehicle has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, showing no discernible signs of use and maintaining a level of aesthetic and mechanical integrity that is rarely encountered on the secondary market. For the discerning individual who accepts no compromise in quality, this offering represents a singular opportunity to acquire a truly pristine asset. Inspection is invited for those who demand the absolute pinnacle of vehicle preservation.",
