    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a ceramic coating that makes the metallic flakes pop under any light. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and supple texture, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or steering wheel. Every electronic feature, from the immersive sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history from authorized dealerships and an engine bay so clean it looks brand new. It comes complete with both original key fobs, all owner's manuals, and a custom-fitted weather cover. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
