      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this specimen, from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior cabin, has been maintained to the most exacting standards. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the sophisticated collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market.",
