      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it practically looks like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it spotless and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and pampered, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
